onent in addition to the dominant disk component. One of the largest and\nhottest high-dispersion patches is present in all age bins, and may be the\nsignature of the end of the long bar.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 12 Feb 2015 21:00:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-23"}
