e is decoupling between the segmental motion of the polymers and the\ntranslational motion of the charge carriers in confinement.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 13 Feb 2015 13:42:30 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 20 Mar 2015 07:17:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-11"}
